The paper presents a scalable dissipative particle dynamics simulation code fully implemented on GPUs using a hybrid CUDA/MPI programming model. The paper discusses the algorithms, numerics, and applications of the code. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science). Other likely sub-categories include cs.MS (Mathematical Software), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), and cs.SC (Scientific Computing).
